data.description: CLOSING COSTS AVAILABE! Welcome to this stunning 3 bed, 2 + bath home in the beautiful neighborhood of Talise de Culebra. This home features an open layout with beautiful 42 inch cabinets, granite countertops, a primary bedroom on the first floor, spacious secondary bedrooms, and an open gameroom/loft  upstairs already wired for surround sound equipment perfect to make it a great media space. This home also has a stunning backyard with an extended covered back patio, fire pit, and beautiful landscaping and freshly stained fence. The neighborhood's amenities include a pool, park, and sports courts for you to enjoy and is just 10 minutes away from 1604 and major retailers/great entertainment. Schedule your showing today!
